Package: serif-apps-suite-xl
Version: 2.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Serif Apps <developer@serifapps.com>
Depends: python3, python3-tk, python3-pil, python3-pil.imagetk, python3-numpy, python3-pygame, vlc, pulseaudio-utils, libasound2-dev
Description: Serif Apps Tactical Desktop Suite
 A unified retro-stylized development and forensic workstation.
 This package installs the Serif Control Hub, alongside five custom
 modules: the Portable Spectral Suite (Microscope), the Retro Image
 Spectrometer (Gloria Lens), the Vector 3D Object Viewer, the retro
 terminal Text Viewer, and the Legacy Theater Player. Early version of serif-apps-arcade is now available!

